<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.8.5">
<l>vaṇaṅkali larakkaṉ cerukkaḷat taviya maṇimuṭi yorupatum puraḷa</l>
<l>vaṇaṅkeḻun tavaṉṟaṉ kavantamniṉ ṟāṭa vamarcceyta vaṭikaḷtam kōyil</l>
<l>piṇaṅkalil neṭuvēy nutimukaṅ kiḻippap piracamvan tiḻitara peruntēṉ</l>
<l>maṇaṅkamaḻ cāral māliruñ cōlai vaṇaṅkutum vāmaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come, simple heart; we will worship at Māliruñcōlai</l>
<l rend="indent">whose slopes are scented by the fragrance of abundant nectar</l>
<l>Since it drips freely, coming from honeycombs</l>
<l rend="indent">when ripped by the pointed tips of tall bamboo [growing] in thickets,</l>
<l>The temple of the god who made war on the battlefield</l>
<l rend="indent">so the unsubmissive demon was crushed,</l>
<l>So that his ten jeweled crowns rolled [and], his spirit having risen,</l>
<l rend="indent">his torso flailed upright.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
